<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/File:SELinux_admin.png" class="image" title="The SELinux administrator in Fedora 8"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/78/SELinux_admin.png/180px-SELinux_admin.png" width="180" height="137" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:SELinux_admin.png" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
The SELinux administrator in <a href="/wiki/Fedora_(operating_system)" title="Fedora (operating system)">Fedora</a> 8</div>
